==English==
===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''windmill''' (''plural'' '''windmills''')

#<!--NMachinery-->A [[machine]] which translates [[linear]] motion of [[wind]] to [[rotational]] motion by means of [[adjustable]] [[vane]]s called [[sail]]s.
#<!--NStructure-->The [[structure]] containing such [[machinery]].
#<!--NToy-->A child's [[toy]] consisting of vanes mounted on a stick that rotate when [[blow]]n by a person or by the wind.
#<!--NBasketball-->A [[dunk]] where the dunker swings his arm in a circular motion before throwing the ball through the hoop.

